Honor your top recipients with a gold and clear award that can be ordered blank or with your organization's logo and name laser engraved on it. Which of your members outshine all the rest?
Price_Includes: laser engraving in a 2.25" x 3.25" area.

Description: If your company end-of-the-year dinners are usually stiff, formal and a bit square, try changing your awards to the Round Glass Trophies! These clear colored awards can smooth out some of those rougher edges and add a beautiful design to your employee recognitions. They measure 7" H x 6" W x 0.6" thick and can be purchased blank or with a laser engraved imprint. Round out the end of your year with handsome trophies that congratulate your company's highest achievers and best employees!
Price_Includes: laser engraving in a 3.5" x 3.5" area.
